{"lemma":"مِقْبَضِ","slug":"مِقْبَضِ","root":"ق.ب.ض","root_slug":"ق-ب-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ب-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35109","n35110","n35111"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%90%D9%82%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"handle"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hilt"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"handpiece"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"occasion, opportunity"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Tool noun from the verb قَبَضَ (qabaḍa, “to grasp”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35109","headword_ar":"مَقْبَضٌ","root":"qbD","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of taking, taking with the hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grasping, clutching, seizing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"receiving:"},{"kind":"text","text":"extr. [in form, for by rule it should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqobiDN","text_ar":"مَقْبِضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M.) See also what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n35110","headword_ar":"مَقْبِضٌ","root":"qbD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Mgh, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqobaDN","text_ar":"مَقْبَضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, M, Msb, K,) but the former is the more common and the better known, (Lth,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqobaDN","text_ar":"مِقْبَضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqobiDapN","text_ar":"مَقْبِضَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqobaDapN","text_ar":"مِقْبَضَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"handle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part where it is grasped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, * Mgh, * Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the whole hand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) of a sword, (S, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaboDapN","text_ar":"قَبْضَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to signify the same; (TA;) or of a knife, (M, A,) and of a bow, (S, A,) and of a whip, (A,) &c., (K,) or of anything: (M:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqobiDapN","text_ar":"مَقْبِضَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqobaDapN","text_ar":"مِقْبَضَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the place of the hand of a spear or spear-shaft: (ISh:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqaAbiDu","text_ar":"مَقَابِضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Mgh","Msb","K","Lth","ISh"]},{"entry_id":"n35111","headword_ar":"مِقْبَضٌ","root":"qbD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqobaDN","text_ar":"مَقْبَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}